title: Dak Prescott, Rockets, time off, 76ers
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Rockets, time off, 76ers
description:
Colin explains why Dak Prescott doesn't have much leverage for the contract he wants, why he's intrigued by the Rockets, NBA players not practicing during the break, and his issues with the 76ers. Guests include Peter Schrager, Kevin O'Connor, Urban Meyer, and Bryan Westbrook.
